(44, 5, 16, 40, 8, 16, 16, 'healed every one', 'Healing and Deliverance Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the healing of the sick and the casting out of unclean spirits. They highlight the miraculous acts performed by Jesus and the apostles, showcasing their authority over illness and demonic forces.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
