(44, 5, 18, 44, 8, 3, 3, NULL, 'Persecution of the Church', 'Both passages emphasize the imprisonment of believers. Acts 5:18 describes the apostles being put in prison, while Acts 8:3 mentions Saul committing men and women to prison.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
